                                                <h4 class="et_pb_module_header">Eric Porper</h4>

                                                &nbsp;
                                                <ul class="et_pb_member_social_links"><li><a href="https://twitter.com/ericporper" class="et_pb_font_icon et_pb_twitter_icon"><span>Twitter</span></a></li></ul>
                                            </div> <!-- .et_pb_team_member_description -->
                                        </div> <!-- .et_pb_team_member -->
                                    </div> <!-- .et_pb_column -->


                                </div> <!-- .et_pb_row --><div class="et_pb_row et_pb_row_19">
                                    <div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4 et_pb_column_35    et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child">


                                        <div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_26 et_pb_bg_layout_light  et_pb_text_align_left">


                                            <div class="et_pb_text_inner">
                                                <h2>A Letter from the organizers</h2>
                                            </div>
                                        </div> <!-- .et_pb_text --><div class="et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_27 et_pb_bg_layout_light  et_pb_text_align_justified">


                                            <div class="et_pb_text_inner">
                                                <div><span style="color: #ffffff; font-size: large;"><span style="font-family: Constantia;">Friends,</span></span></div>
                                                <p><span style="font-size: large;"> </span></p>
                                                <div><span style="color: #ffffff; font-size: large;"><span style="font-family: Constantia;">We wanted to take a moment to cordially invite you to an annual event in one of the most exciting markets in the United States &#8211; Atlanta! As founders of Cryptolina, one of the earliest and longest running Blockchain and Cryptocurrency conferences on the East Coast, we are proud to announce our inaugural expansion beyond the borders of North Carolina to bring you the ATLANTA BLOCKCHAIN EXPERIENCE!</span></span></div>
                                                <p><span style="font-size: large;"> </span></p>
                                                <div><span style="color: #ffffff; font-size: large;"><span style="font-family: Constantia;">We are more determined than ever to bring technology centers like Atlanta pertinent and important industry debate and discussion.  Our focus has been from the start on educating and promoting Blockchain and Cryptocurrency technologies to markets that often are overlooked and underserved. Atlanta is ready for its first major conference considering that some of the biggest names in Technology and Blockchain are local! </span><span style="font-family: Constantia;">Atlanta and the surrounding communities represent the future of innovation and technology and we are committed to making this year’s event a true standout event. We are determined to continue delivering on our goals of promoting the virtuous aspects of Blockchain in a setting where the most cutting edge discussions, networking, and synergies can be achieved.</span></span></div>
                                                <p><span style="font-size: large;"> </span></p>
                                                <p><span style="color: #ffffff; font-size: large;"><span style="font-family: Constantia;">The Atlanta Blockchain Experience conference will continue the efforts of our North Carolina events to bring top experts, key figures, and innovative thinkers to participate in what many have called the best Blockchain conference in the East Coast.</span></span></p>
                                                <div><span style="color: #ffffff; font-size: large;"><span style="font-family: Constantia;">We welcome you to the first ever Atlanta Blockchain Conference to participate as a valued guest, speaker, sponsor, and/or panelist.  This event will be the largest general Blockchain technology conference in the Metropolitan Atlanta area, and we are thrilled to welcome each and every one of you!</span></span></div>
                                                <p><span style="font-size: large;"> </span></p>
                                                <div><span style="color: #ffffff; font-size: large;"><span style="font-family: Constantia;">Sincerely,</span></span></div>
                                                <p><span style="font-size: large;"> </span></p>
                                                <div><span style="color: #ffffff; font-size: large;"><span style="font-family: Constantia;">Faruk Okcetin</span></span></div>
                                                <div><span style="color: #ffffff; font-size: large;"><span style="font-family: Constantia;">Rich Spuller</span></span></div>
                                                <div><span style="color: #ffffff; font-size: large;"><span style="font-family: Constantia;">Eric Porper</span></span></div>
                                                <div></div>
                                                <div><span style="color: #ffffff; font-family: Constantia; font-size: large;">Organizers of Cryptolina and the Atlanta Blockchain Experience</span></div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div> <!-- .et_pb_text -->
                                    </div> <!-- .et_pb_column -->


                                </div> <!-- .et_pb_row --><div class="et_pb_row et_pb_row_20">
